snippet.title: Titanic Demo 401 - Official Update Trailer
snippet.description:
Containing roughly 50% of the RMS TITANIC, our next update of DEMO 401 will be our largest and most detailed recreation yet!

For progress updates on the full experience, TITANIC: PROJECT 401
visit our PATREON - https://www.patreon.com/TitanicHG

And follow us everywhere else!
WEBSITE - https://www.titanichg.com
FACEBOOK - https://www.facebook.com/TitanicHG
INSTAGRAM - https://www.instagram.com/Titanic.HG
TWITTER - https://twitter.com/TitanicHG

Trailer Cinematics Recorded by our Media Manager Jack and Derek Verveer
Edited by James Penca
Music by @anthonycasalena3828 
Listen to the full piece here: https://youtu.be/qw71Tw32sis
